text: Ærest of Cirichylle on horgan sloh thanon on beorhleage, thanon on west mæd ufewearde, thanon on bydeburnan, thanon on anna mapulder thanon on bilian wyrthe, swa forth on hagan, thæt on beorreding mæd northewearde, thanon on tha greatan ac, thæt forth on hagan oth stanbroc.

Thonon on hean wifeleshylle oth thone ealdan weg andlang weges oth fyldena wylle, thanon on thone ealdan hagan, thæt swa forth ut on bealtunes ersc nytheweardne thonon on æscleage of tham æsce forth on hagan on gerihte ut on feld on anne stan, thæt swa forth east andlang weges eft on ciric hylle.
